7db29e|\n|-\n|rowspan=4|''Tales from<br>Harrow<br>County:<br>Death's<br>Choir''\n|#1<ref>{{cite web|title=Tales from Harrow County: Death's Choir #1|url=https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3004-146/Tales-from-Harrow-County-Deaths-Choir-1|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=23 September 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Tales from Harrow County: Death's Choir #1 (Tyler Crook variant cover)|url=https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3006-423/Tales-from-Harrow-County-Deaths-Choir-1-Tyler-Crook-Variant-Cover|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=23 September 2019}}</ref>\n|December 18, 2019\n|rowspan=4|Cullen Bunn<br>''and'' Tyler Crook\n|rowspan=4|Naomi Franquiz<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">LETTERING:</span>''' Tyler Crook<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">COVERS:</span>''' Naomi Franquiz<br>Tyler Crook <span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">(variants)</span>\n|rowspan=4|\u2014\n|-\n|#2<ref>{{cite web|title=Tales from Harrow County: Death's Choir #2|url=https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3004-147/Tales-from-Harrow-County-Deaths-Choir-2|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=31 October 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Tales from Harrow County: Death's Choir #2 (Tyler Crook variant cover)|url=https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3006-424/Tales-from-Harrow-County-Deaths-Choir-2-Tyler-Crook-Variant-Cover|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=31 October 2019}}</ref>\n|January 15, 2020\n|-\n|#3\n|February 12, 2020\n|-\n|#4\n|March 11, 2020\n|}\n\n===Trade paperbacks===\nFour months after each arc of ''Harrow County'' wrapped up, it was collected in trade paperback.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!colspan=6|Trade paperbacks\n|-\n!Volume\n!Title\n!Release Date\n!Material collected\n!Extras\n!ISBN\n|-\n|colspan=6 style=background:#bc4026|\n|-\n|1\n|''Harrow County:<br>Countless Haints''<ref>{{cite web|title=Harrow County \u2013 Volume 1: Countless Haints|url=http://