s'' by Ma'at Crook\n|-\n|colspan=6 style=background:#e18592|\n|-\n|rowspan=4|''Harrow<br>County:<br>Dark Times<br>A\u2019Coming''\n|#25<ref>{{cite web|title=Harrow County #25|url=http://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3000-443/Harrow-County-25|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=31 May 2017}}</ref>\n|September 13, 2017\n|rowspan=4|Cullen Bunn\n|rowspan=4|Tyler Crook\n|\n*''Granddad's Rocking Chair'' by Ma'at Crook\n|-\n|#26<ref>{{cite web|title=Harrow County #26|url=http://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3000-737/Harrow-County-26|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=17 August 2017}}</ref>\n|October 11, 2017\n|\n*''Tales of Harrow County: Exterminator''<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">STORY:</span>''' Tyler Crook<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">ART:</span>''' Alise Glu\u0161kova\n|-\n|#27<ref>{{cite web|title=Harrow County #27|url=https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3000-738/Harrow-County-27|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=14 December 2017}}</ref>\n|November 8, 2017\n|\n*''Tales of Harrow County: Combine''<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">STORY:</span>''' Tyler Crook<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">ART:</span>''' Alise Glu\u0161kova\n|-\n|#28<ref>{{cite web|title=Harrow County #28|url=https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3000-739/Harrow-County-28|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=14 December 2017}}</ref>\n|December 13, 2017\n|\n*''Tales of Harrow County: The Radio''<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">STORY:</span>''' Rhiannon Rasmussen-Silverstein<br>'''<span style=\"font-size: 75%;\">ART:</span>''' Christianne Goudreau\n|-\n|colspan=6 style=background:#adbe62|\n|-\n|rowspan=4|''Harrow<br>County:<br>Done<br>Come<br>Back''\n|#29<ref>{{cite web|title=Harrow County #29|url=https://www.darkhorse.com/Comics/3000-740/Harrow-County-29|website=DarkHorse.com|publisher=Dark Horse Comics|accessdate=11 January 2018}}</ref>\n|March 21, 2018\n|rowspan=4|Cullen Bunn\n|rowsp